headline: This Energy Stock Rocketed More Than 100% in 2024. Does It Have the Fuel to Continue Rallying in 2025?
summary: Shares of Targa Resources (NYSE: TRGP) were blistering hot in 2024.  The midstream company was up more than 105% heading into the final trading days of the year.  Add in its dividend, and the total return was even higher.
